在夜色中。","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"意识形态谬论","slug":"意识形态谬论","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/tags/%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%B0%AC%E8%AE%BA/"},{"name":"Rm","slug":"Rm","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/tags/Rm/"}]},{"title":"意识形态谬论-主线","slug":"意识形态谬论-主线","date":"2022-01-12T13:24:04.000Z","updated":"2022-01-12T13:27:27.634Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/01/12/意识形态谬论-主线/","link":"","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/2022/01/12/%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%B0%AC%E8%AE%BA-%E4%B8%BB%E7%BA%BF/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"意识形态谬论","slug":"意识形态谬论","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/tags/%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%B0%AC%E8%AE%BA/"},{"name":"BZJR","slug":"BZJR","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/tags/BZJR/"}]},{"title":"意识形态谬论-东亚史","slug":"意识形态谬论-东亚史","date":"2022-01-12T13:22:55.000Z","updated":"2022-01-12T13:27:00.787Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/01/12/意识形态谬论-东亚史/","link":"","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/2022/01/12/%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%B0%AC%E8%AE%BA-%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%9A%E5%8F%B2/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"意识形态谬论","slug":"意识形态谬论","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/tags/%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%B0%AC%E8%AE%BA/"},{"name":"BZJR","slug":"BZJR","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/tags/BZJR/"}]},{"title":"意识形态谬论-名词/人物","slug":"意识形态谬论-名词-人物","date":"2022-01-12T13:14:08.000Z","updated":"2022-01-12T15:26:37.868Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/01/12/意识形态谬论-名词-人物/","link":"","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/2022/01/12/%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%B0%AC%E8%AE%BA-%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D-%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9/","excerpt":"","text":"东亚苏维埃修正主义共和国联盟(UEASRR)成员国: 东约(东太平洋公约组织,EPTO)IChO(国际氢弹制造组织)SSH: Soviet, Soaring Hell STERIN: Soviet Trotskyism Eternally Remains In Nature!","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"意识形态谬论","slug":"意识形态谬论","permalink":"https://revisionism.cf/tags/%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%B0%AC%E8%AE%BA/"},{"name":"BZJR",